ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Designating the President of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada as the appropriate Minister for the purposes of the Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing Order in Council P.C. 2013-303 of March 19, 2013; and (2) designating the President of the Queen's Privy Council for Canada as the appropriate Minister with respect to the Canadian Transportation Accident Investigation and Safety Board for the purposes of the Financial Administration Act.
